## 📄 File 5: .gitignore

```gitignore
# VirtualBox files
*.vdi
*.vbox
*.vbox-prev
*.vmdk

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble

# Linux
.directory
*.swp
*.swo

# Windows
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Kali session logs
script*.txt
session_*.log

# Packet captures
*.pcap
*.pcapng

# Nmap outputs (if you commit them, remove these lines)
*.nmap
*.xml
*.gnmap

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-*

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
